      <title>开始新的一天需要知道的五件事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-01-03/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早上好。在经历了今年历史上最糟糕的开局之一之后，美国国债和股市再次下跌，几分钟后美联储公布了数据，本周末将公布就业数据。这就是市场的动因。 —萨姆·昂斯特德]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-01-03/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚取消加密货币禁令后对银行实施严格规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/nigeria-slaps-strict-rules-on-banks-after-lifting-cryptocurrency-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚中央银行发布了针对银行开设加密货币账户的首个指导方针，同时保留了禁止银行以自己的名义持有或交易虚拟资产的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/nigeria-slaps-strict-rules-on-banks-after-lifting-cryptocurrency-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
