    <item>
      <title>英国债务面临供应墙在全球债券低迷中遭受更严重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/uk-debt-facing-wall-of-supply-hit-harder-in-global-bond-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国长期债券是受全球债务市场低迷打击最严重的债券之一，投资者为本月晚些时候的一系列英国国债销售腾出了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/uk-debt-facing-wall-of-supply-hit-harder-in-global-bond-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:10:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>失业的美国人在强劲的就业市场中被遗忘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/unemployed-struggle-to-pay-high-prices-in-strong-us-job-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出人意料的强劲美国就业市场正在帮助普通美国人保持支出，同时及时了解账单情况。在亚特兰大，平均水平对于像拉伦·埃斯库这样的人来说并没有多少安慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/unemployed-struggle-to-pay-high-prices-in-strong-us-job-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券先于美国数据下跌 10年期国债收益率展望4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/treasury-10-year-yield-eyes-4-as-bonds-dip-ahead-of-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债市场连续第四天延续跌势，10年期国债收益率接近4%，反映出投资者在新经济数据和美联储会议纪要发布前的谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/treasury-10-year-yield-eyes-4-as-bonds-dip-ahead-of-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，VinFast 计划于 2024 年在印度南部建设电池厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/vinfast-is-said-to-plan-battery-plant-in-southern-india-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，VinFast Auto Ltd. 计划今年在印度南部泰米尔纳德邦建立一家电池制造厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/vinfast-is-said-to-plan-battery-plant-in-southern-india-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着财政紧缩迫在眉睫，印度尼西亚着眼于更高的早期债务销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/indonesia-eyes-higher-early-debt-sales-as-tighter-finances-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球经济疲软和大宗商品价格疲软限制了收入和资金流入，今年印尼财政可能会收紧，因此印度尼西亚正在提前发行债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/indonesia-eyes-higher-early-debt-sales-as-tighter-finances-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:24:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度称俄罗斯石油进口下降并非由于支付困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/india-says-russian-oil-import-drop-not-due-to-payment-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油部长哈迪普·辛格·普里(Hardeep Singh Puri)表示，印度炼油商减少了从俄罗斯的石油进口，因为货物折扣不具吸引力，他驳斥了因支付相关挑战而导致流量下降的说法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/india-says-russian-oil-import-drop-not-due-to-payment-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最高法院免除阿达尼对兴登堡传奇的更多调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/top-india-court-asks-sebi-to-close-adani-probe-in-three-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院命令该国市场监管机构在三个月内完成对阿达尼集团的调查，并表示不再需要进行更多调查，这为这位因“真相”盛行而欢呼判决的亿万富翁缓了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/top-india-court-asks-sebi-to-close-adani-probe-in-three-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
